  "legend": "Command Squads accompany a Chapter’s high-ranking officers. These veterans and specialists serve as honour guards and provide vital support to a commander. Champions defend their Company with martial excellence, Ancients guard its inspirational relic banners and Apothecaries tend to injuries or preserve the gene-seed of the fallen.",
